snippet.title: Olaf the Boozer - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
You wake up with a hangover, a trashed tavern, and a furious barkeep. Who's to blame? Spoiler: everyone, but especially you. Solve sokoban puzzles, dive into a medieval party vibe, and experience that post-hangover "what happened?" feeling. #indiegames #steamnextfest #sokoban

Check out Demo of Olaf the Boozer on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3528050/Olaf_the_Boozer_Demo/
